Depends: ${misc:Depends}, nodejs | nodejs-22 | nodejs-24 | nodejs-25 | nodejs-26
Description: Zero-runtime-dependency package manager bridge for Node.js
 Corepack is a zero-runtime-dependency Node.js script that acts as a bridge
 between Node.js projects and the package managers they are intended to be
 used with during development.
